title: Kyle Durfey from Pianos Become the Teeth
itunes:title: Kyle Durfey from Pianos Become the Teeth
description:
This week I have Kyle, the vocalist from Pianos Become the Teeth, on the show. I have a strong affinity for the band and was excited to find out more about Kyle and his life. We discussed misconceptions of the band and Kyle specifically, how AWFUL the recording process is and growing up. This episode is brought to you exclusively by Topshelf Records and their upcoming release from You Blew It! Visit topshelfrecords.com for more information. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
